# Employee Knowledge Engine

See [EMPLOYEE_KNOWLEDGE_ENGINE.md](../../EMPLOYEE_KNOWLEDGE_ENGINE.md).

## Rules

1. Only learn from administrator-approved sources — transparency mandatory.
2. Role-based access via `knowledge_permissions`; owners/admins see all categories.
3. Employee assistant provides guidance — humans make final decisions.
4. Low confidence (&lt;50%) triggers gap detection and escalation recommendation.
5. Full audit via `employee_knowledge_audit_logs`; platform sees aggregates only.
6. Route: `/app/settings/employee-knowledge` (spec `/admin/employee-knowledge`).
7. i18n: `customerApp.employeeKnowledge.*`, `platform.employeeKnowledge.*` in en/no/sv/da.
8. Integrates Business DNA (`support_knowledge_items`) as fallback for support procedures.

## Tables

`eke_settings` · `employee_knowledge_items` · `knowledge_permissions` · `employee_knowledge_sources` · `employee_knowledge_gaps` · `employee_onboarding_paths` · `employee_onboarding_progress` · `employee_knowledge_audit_logs`
